Subject: drm/amdgpu: disable agp for sriov
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 81c274c473a25e7e86540cdeaa181421e7daafff
